<main
  class="flex bg-secondary flex-col items-center justify-center w-full px-4 lg:px-20 pt-8 md:pt-16 lg:mt-8"
  id="about"
  style="height: fit-content"
>
  <div
    class="w-full md:flex-row items-center gap-6 md:[&>*]:px-12 [&>*]:px-4 [&>*]:py-8 flex flex-col mt-8"
  >
    <div
      class="border-2 border-gray-200 flex p-0 md:p-2 flex-col md:max-w-1/2 w-full rounded-xl h-full"
    >
      <h1 class="font-bold text-xl">Who I am</h1>
      <span class="mt-4 w-full"
        >I'm a seasoned full-stack developer has experience in crafting robust
        and scalable web applications. My passion lies in solving complex
        problems and leveraging cutting-edge technologies to build innovative
        solutions. With a strong foundation in both front-end and back-end
        development, I bring a holistic approach to every project I undertake.</span
      >
    </div>
    <div class="border-gray-200 border-2 rounded-xl w-full md:max-w-1/2 p-2">
      <h1 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">Professional Summary</h1>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 md:ml-0 sm:px-4 md:px-1 flex flex-col md:gap-2">
        <li>Expertise in Python, React, Node.js, and cloud technologies.</li>
        <li>Strong background in database design and optimization.</li>
        <li>Follows best development practices.</li>
        <li>Experience with Agile methodologies and team leadership.</li>
        <li>Passionate about clean code and software architecture.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-2 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm w-full mt-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 ml-4">Work Experience</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-l-2 border-gray-400 pl-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">
          Software Developer Engineer Intern
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Blue Mango Labs</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Jan 2024 - Dec 2024</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
        Developed a high-performance REST API for an astrology app using
        FastAPI, processing 100K+ daily requests with a 40% reduction in
        response times. Designed scalable real-time solutions, integrating
        LiveKit for video/voice calls and EMQX for messaging, supporting 10K+
        concurrent users with sub-100ms latency.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

